---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const standingsSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Dataset",
  "name": "CONMEBOL World Cup 2026 Qualification Standings",
  "description": "Live points table and goal difference for the South American World Cup qualifiers."
};

const fetchStandings = async () => {
  return [
    { rank: 1, team: "Argentina", points: 38, played: 18, gd: 20 },
    { rank: 2, team: "Uruguay", points: 34, played: 18, gd: 15 },
    { rank: 3, team: "Colombia", points: 32, played: 18, gd: 10 },
    { rank: 4, team: "Brazil", points: 29, played: 18, gd: 8 },
    { rank: 5, team: "Ecuador", points: 28, played: 18, gd: 5 },
    { rank: 6, team: "Venezuela", points: 24, played: 18, gd: -2 },
  ];
};

const standings = await fetchStandings();
---

<Layout 
  title="CONMEBOL Standings: FIFA World Cup 2026 Qualifiers Table" 
  description="South American qualifiers are brutal. Check the live CONMEBOL standings to see which nations are booking their tickets to North America."
  schema={standingsSchema}
>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-blue-900 tracking-tight">CONMEBOL Standings: The Toughest Path to 2026</h1>
  
  <article class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none mb-10 text-gray-700">
    <p>South American qualifiers are a bloodbath. There's no polite way to put it. You travel to play at 3,600 meters of altitude in La Paz, you lose. You play in the suffocating humidity of Barranquilla, you cramp up. It's the ultimate test of endurance.</p>
    
    <p>With the 2026 expansion, FIFA threw CONMEBOL a bone: six direct qualification spots and one playoff ticket. But don't let that fool you into thinking it's easy. The margins are razor-thin. One bad international break and a powerhouse can drop out of the top six.</p>
    
    <p>Here is the raw data. The definitive table that dictates who survives and who watches the tournament from the couch.</p>
  </article>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto shadow-md rounded-xl border border-gray-200 mb-8">
    <table class="min-w-full bg-white text-left text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white font-semibold">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-6 py-4">Pos</th>
          <th class="px-6 py-4">Nation</th>
          <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center">Played</th>
          <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center">GD</th>
          <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-blue-300">PTS</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
        {standings.map((team, index) => (
          <tr class={`hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors ${index < 6 ? 'border-l-4 border-l-green-500' : index === 6 ? 'border-l-4 border-l-yellow-400' : ''}`}>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-gray-500">{team.rank}</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">{team.team}</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">{team.played}</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-500">{team.gd > 0 ? `+${team.gd}` : team.gd}</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-black text-lg">{team.points}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">* Green line: Direct Qualification. Yellow line: Inter-confederation play-off.</p>
</Layout>